<br>
it has been 3 expansions...that does not mean we need to upgrade the epic, it means we need to move on.  Verant clearly said at the FanFaire (forget where i saw this posted, it's all around tho) that any epic that is still a great item today was overpowered to begin with, implying that the epics that are now sub-par items are working as intended.<br>
